OL,3,CFamilies 'face typical #1,145 bill per
OL,4,Cchild for holiday clubs over summer'
OL,6,FFamilies are facing a typical summer
OL,7,Fholiday club bill of #1,145 per child,
OL,8,Fa report has found.
OL,10,FOn average, holiday childcare costs
OL,11,Facross Britain have risen by 5% in the
OL,12,Fpast year, leaving working parents
OL,13,Ffacing an average bill of nearly #191
OL,14,Fper child per week.
OL,16,FThis equates to around #1,145 for a
OL,17,Fsix-week summer holiday, according to
OL,18,Fresearch by the Coram Family and
OL,19,FChildcare charity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
