FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784236711
OL,3,CFamilies 'face typical #1,145 bill per
OL,4,Cchild for holiday clubs over summer'
OL,6,FThe report said: "Parents and carers
OL,7,Fpay much more for childcare during the
OL,8,Fholidays than during term time.
OL,10,F"In Great Britain, a week at a holiday
OL,11,Fclub costs over 2.7 times more than an
OL,12,Fafter school club, #191 per week
OL,13,Fcompared to #70."
OL,15,FIn Wales, average prices have surged
OL,16,Fby 10% annually to reach nearly #224
OL,17,Fper week, according to the research.
OL,19,FHoliday club prices were also found to
OL,20,Fhave risen by 16% in inner London and
OL,21,Fby 12% in the North East.
OL,26,@nD@ROUrD@AOUuD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784236711
OL,3,CFamilies 'face typical #1,145 bill per
OL,4,Cchild for holiday clubs over summer'
OL,6,FBucking the trend, prices in Yorkshire
OL,7,Fand the Humber fell by 1% typically,
OL,8,Fthe report found.
OL,10,FThe holiday childcare survey 2026 is
OL,11,Fbased on surveys from local
OL,12,Fauthorities in England, Scotland and
OL,13,FWales, which were returned to Coram
OL,14,FFamily and Childcare between April and
OL,15,FJune 2026.
OL,17,FSome 199 local authorities returned
OL,18,Fdata.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
