OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784236711
OL,3,CFamilies 'face typical #1,145 bill per
OL,4,Cchild for holiday clubs over summer'
OL,6,FThis report looked at the costs of
OL,7,Fchildcare and the availability of
OL,8,Fchildcare in Britain for children aged
OL,9,Ffour to 14-years-old.
OL,11,FLydia Hodges, head of Coram Family and
OL,12,FChildcare, said: "Holiday childcare is
OL,13,Fessential for parents to take and stay
OL,14,Fin work but, for too many families,
OL,15,Fthe six-week break brings a sharp
OL,16,Fincrease in childcare costs.
OL,26,@tD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784236711
OL,3,CFamilies 'face typical #1,145 bill per
OL,4,Cchild for holiday clubs over summer'
OL,6,F"Cost is only part of the challenge.
OL,7,FWhen we asked councils whether there
OL,8,Fis enough holiday childcare in their
OL,9,Farea, the most frequent response was
OL,10,Fthat they do not know.
OL,12,F"We heard this answer much more
OL,13,Ffrequently than when we asked the same
OL,14,Fquestions about pre-school childcare
OL,15,Ffor our childcare survey this spring."
OL,17,FThe report also found that a week of
OL,18,Fholiday childcare with a childminder
OL,19,Fcosts around #251 on average, marking
OL,20,Fan increase of 7%.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
