OL,3,CFamilies 'face typical #1,145 bill per
OL,4,Cchild for holiday clubs over summer'
OL,6,FThe report looks at costs before the
OL,7,Fsupport available to help pay for
OL,8,Fchildcare is taken into account,
OL,9,Fallowing it to track changes in costs
OL,10,Fover time and recognising that
OL,11,Ffamilies can be eligible for different
OL,12,Flevels of support depending on their
OL,13,Fcircumstances.
OL,15,FHere are the average costs per week of
OL,16,Fholiday clubs followed by
OL,17,Fchildminders, according to the
OL,18,Fresearch:
OL,20,FBritain, #190.77, #251.48
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
